  "helpFaqA3": "Yes — go to Profile → Settings → Theme and choose Light, Dark, or System to follow your device automatically.",
  "helpFaqQ4": "How do I change the app language?",
  "helpFaqA4": "Go to Profile → Settings → Language, or use the language toggle shown on the sign-in and onboarding screens.",
